<br>
He filled his plate with the precious ambrosia, food of the gods and then filled his goblet with wine.  His eyes always attentive to the activity in the room, always watching, always cautiously alert.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 338<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(9/19/02 12:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=270.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://web.uvic.ca/grs/bowman/myth/images/haifa/h89.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Let me talk to you.</span><hr size=1> As he looks Gaia appears by the rulers of the universe side. She greeted Zeus and Hera yet failed to greet him. Poseidon's heart almost sank and he addressed Gaia with a look of suprise on his face. &quot;Grandmother? No greetings for me? I am quite shocked but I suppose something presses you so that you must speak with these two!&quot; He smiles and shrugs off his disappointment. After that he embraces Gaia in a hug and kisses her cheek. &quot;I'm glad you could find time to come anyway Gaia.&quot; <br>
<br>
Hecate arrives just as Poseidon's thoughts begin to drift from her to making some conversation with the others. He takes her hand into his and kisses the back of it. &quot;Took you long enough Hecate. I was beginning to wonder if you had wandered off.&quot; His arm wraps around her shoulders and he whispers to her, &quot;Come let us sit at that table over there where we can talk alone.&quot; <br>
<br>
Then looing to the others he says, &quot;Excuse Hecate and I we need to catch up it won't be too long. Enjoy the feast.&quot; At his bidding one of Hephaestus' tables rolls over and the God places the empty goblet down onto it. It rolls away and Poseidon urges Hecate to come with him to sit. <br>
<br>
&quot;Ah yes Athena no hard feelings right? It was not my intention that things go about as wayward as they did.&quot; he lied about the Hephaestus nearly raping her. He did not mention the details so that the others would not know of it. &quot;If you need to speak to me please do come and I shall explain myself after Hecate and I are through.&quot;<br>
<br>
With that he headed off with the goddess Hecate to the table. <p>Poseidon~Lord of the Deep Blue Sea~Patron Of Horses And Sailors~</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=hypnos>Hypnos </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.backtalk.org/shadowydreamer/anime/zagato1.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 318<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(9/19/02 2:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=270.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> *whispering in Athena's ear* </span><hr size=1> ***Hypnos did not appear at first but only mad his voice in Athena's ear.***  <br>
